{"tid":1459662,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我地嘅對手係中共！","createTime":"2019-08-12T18:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T20:40:49.000Z","uid":289289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7984b86baa1d1a34f91cc1ef49cbf57e58a7c549","tid":1459662,"uid":289289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:51:52.000Z","msg":"大家有留意國新辦記者會嗎，佢想話我地係恐怖分子。<br />\n唔可以比佢咁樣老屈我地，連儂牆同機場文宣組請參考！幫中共果d要叫做<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">親政府極端恐怖主義</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢種主義特色係<br />\n1.民智未開，沒有獨立思考，一旦冇左政府就等於冇思想<br />\n<br />\n2.祟尚權貴，佢地熱心於支持比平民高一級嘅平民，總之有權力管理社智嘅人，低至一個警員，高至國家主席。<br />\n<br />\n3.有持無恐，各得自己係支持有權力嘅人就可以乜都做得，包括殺人放火強姦<br />\n<br />\n4.毫無人道主義，只要認為你係犯罪就覺得你乜都冇資格去擁有任何罰，包括公平同尊嚴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n令外轉貼一則形勢分析<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ktabZNftdKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FktabZNftdKE&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB20yCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=480eff20\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ktabZNftdKE</a>"},{"pid":"fa7dcb3050b401b988afe9975370bdbb56d441ee","tid":1459662,"uid":289289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T18:52:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1abd3ad371cfc1c3e1e3a9f2abefaa9365a82b5","tid":1459662,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAVAL0G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAVAL0G.jpg&h=91da0cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWMcOd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWMcOd1.jpg&h=bbad276f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m6Ggvsn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm6Ggvsn.jpg&h=03091cda&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HDOKEkH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHDOKEkH.jpg&h=b1291acd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"ht